{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" objects. When the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Keep this property set to ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the view’s legibility is important.","type":"text"}]},{"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views."}]}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)scalesWithViewingDistance","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L180","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"}},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tilted map."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"title":"MLNAnnotationImage","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}]}}}